data.description: Step into luxury living on a double lot! This meticulously maintained 4/3/2 CBS CUSTOM HOME offers resort-style amenities including an underground saltwater heated pool with hot tub and a built in water slide, second driveway, and lighted basketball court. With vaulted ceilings, abundant natural light, and a flexible split bedroom plan, this home is perfect for relaxation and entertaining. Enjoy granite countertops, maple cabinets, and a cozy breakfast bar in the kitchen, while the master suite impresses with a tray ceiling, walk-in closet, and roman tub. With 2,359 sq.ft. under air and a 20,909 sq.ft. outdoor space, this property offers ample room for enjoyment and endless possibilities. Don't miss out on this exquisite opportunity!
